{"lemma":"مَحاسِنِ","slug":"مَحاسِنِ","root":"ح.س.ن","root_slug":"ح-س-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-س-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8031"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B3%D9%90%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"good qualities, merits, charms, positives, pros, advantages"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8031","headword_ar":"مَحَاسِنُ","root":"Hsn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beautiful places"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parts"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) accord. to some, (TA,) the sing. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHosanN","text_ar":"مَحْسَنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": or it has no sing.: (K:) the former opinion is disapproved by ISd.: the latter is the opinion of the grammarians and of the generality of the lexicologists: and therefore, says Sb, the rel. n. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAsiniY~N","text_ar":"مَحَاسِنِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for if"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAsinu","text_ar":"مَحَاسِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"had a sing., it would be restored to the sing. in forming the rel. n. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnapu kaviyrapu AlmaHaAsini","text_ar":"فُلَانَةُ كَثِيرَةُ المَحَاسِنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a woman has many beautiful places"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parts"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAsinu Alwajohi","text_ar":"مَحَاسِنُ الوَجْهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa masaAwiyhi","text_ar":"وَ مَسَاوِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beauties of the face, and its defects"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lmH","text_ar":"لمح"},{"kind":"text","text":":) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAsinu","text_ar":"مَحَاسِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaAwK","text_ar":"مَسَاوٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-  [As contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaAwK","text_ar":"مَسَاوٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Good qualities of any kind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good actions;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasanaAtN","text_ar":"حَسَنَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": agreeably with an explanation in the KL,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nykwy^yhA","text_ar":"نيكوييها"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusonN","text_ar":"حُسْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b4-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHosanapN","text_ar":"مَحْسَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}